fields.description:
Running an existing (vanilla Titanium) app with the following in the app.js file:

{code:javascript}var doNotBackUp = Titanium.Filesystem.getFile(Titanium.Filesystem.applicationDataDirectory);
doNotBackUp.remoteBackup = false;{code}

Results in the following error: 

{code}<Warning>: [ERROR] Application received error: Error setting remote backup flag: at app.js (line 1){code}
